    <section id="fs-id1169737803624" type="problems-exercises" class="problems-exercises"><title>Problems &amp; Exercises</title><exercise id="fs-id1169738079808" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id1169738079810">    <para id="import-auto-id1169736678323">(a) Two microwave frequencies are authorized for use in microwave ovens: 900 and 2560 MHz. Calculate the wavelength of each. (b) Which frequency would produce smaller hot spots in foods due to interference effects?</para>
